sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Researcher
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant Celery as Celery Worker
    participant Seg as Segmentation
    participant Feat as Feature Extractor
    participant Qdrant as Qdrant DB
    participant PG as PostgreSQL

    User->>FE: Upload image + strain + media
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/images/upload (FormData)
    API->>PG: Create image record
    API-->>FE: { image_id, job_id, status: pending_segmentation }

    API->>Celery: Dispatch segmentation task
    Celery->>Seg: Run KMeans/Contour segmentation
    Seg-->>Celery: [{ bbox, crop_path }]
    Celery->>PG: Create segment records
    Celery->>PG: Update job status

    FE->>API: Poll GET /api/v1/jobs/{job_id}
    API-->>FE: { status: segments_ready }

    FE->>API: GET /api/v1/images/{id}/segments
    API-->>FE: [{ segment_id, bbox, crop_url }]

    FE->>User: Display bbox overlay on image
    User->>FE: Edit bboxes (resize, move, add, delete)
    FE->>API: PATCH /api/v1/images/{id}/segments
    API->>PG: Update segment records

    User->>FE: Click "Process Retrieval"
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/retrieval/query
    API->>Celery: Dispatch retrieval task
    API-->>FE: { job_id, status: processing }

    Celery->>Feat: Extract features per segment
    Feat-->>Celery: Feature vectors (1280-dim)
    Celery->>Qdrant: KNN search (k=5, cosine)
    Qdrant-->>Celery: Top-k neighbors
    Celery->>Celery: Apply env strategy filter
    Celery->>Celery: Aggregate species scores
    Celery->>PG: Save retrieval results

    FE->>API: GET /api/v1/retrieval/jobs/{id}/results
    API->>PG: Fetch ranked results + neighbor details
    API-->>FE: { rankings: [{ rank, species, score, neighbors }] }
    FE->>User: Display ranked results table
